casebody.data:
Fred GRAY, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee. No. 4D17-3527 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fourth District. [April 17, 2019] Fred Gray, Quincy, pro se. No appearance for appellee. ON REMAND FROM THE SUPREME COURT OF FLORIDA Per Curiam.

Upon remand from the Florida Supreme Court, we reverse appellant's sentence in accordance with State v. Lewars , 259 So.3d 793 (Fla. 2018), and remand for resentencing.

Warner, Conner and Kuntz, JJ., concur.
